1
00:00:30,625 --> 00:00:32,208
Heads up, Ganta!

2
00:00:40,333 --> 00:00:41,000
[OHARA]
Karako!

3
00:00:41,083 --> 00:00:42,041
What are you doing?!

4
00:00:42,125 --> 00:00:43,625
Don't stand around!
Get out of here!

5
00:00:43,708 --> 00:00:45,333
No, you--Wait!

6
00:00:45,416 --> 00:00:46,833
We can take the
sonofabitch down!

7
00:00:46,916 --> 00:00:48,041
[AKIYAMA]
There isn't time! Forget it!

8
00:00:48,125 --> 00:00:50,541
[GANTA]
We can't leave her!

9
00:00:50,625 --> 00:00:52,458
Karako!

10
00:00:56,083 --> 00:00:59,125
It's all you... Ganta.

11
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:05,916
[BELL CHIMES]

12
00:01:07,250 --> 00:01:12,208
♪ opening song ♪

13
00:02:38,166 --> 00:02:39,625
[MATAYOSHI]
Karako Koshio, huh...?

14
00:02:39,708 --> 00:02:41,208
The "Game Fowl" herself...

15
00:02:41,291 --> 00:02:44,166
[KOUMOTO] Who makes a nutcase
their damn second-in-command?

16
00:02:44,250 --> 00:02:47,041
Seriously, did Nagi lose
his marbles or something?

17
00:02:47,125 --> 00:02:49,208
[ENDOU] I'd keep it
down if I were you...

18
00:02:49,291 --> 00:02:51,500
If there's a cockfight,
she's gonna win.

19
00:02:51,583 --> 00:02:54,041
[OHARA]
She can totally hear you!

20
00:02:54,125 --> 00:03:00,041
[BELL CHIMES]

21
00:03:00,125 --> 00:03:02,291
[NAGI]
What a beautiful sound.

22
00:03:04,666 --> 00:03:07,666
It's a cheap little
bell--dime a dozen.

23
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:11,666
And yet it
lends me assurance.

24
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,708
However grim
the circumstances...

25
00:03:13,791 --> 00:03:16,916
if the chiming of that little
bell can reach my ears...

26
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:21,125
then I'll know that quite
a woman has my back.

27
00:03:21,208 --> 00:03:23,291
[NAGI] It warms me
like the light of day,

28
00:03:23,375 --> 00:03:26,791
even in the darkness
of this basement.

29
00:03:26,875 --> 00:03:29,416
Who ever said I was
joining up, smooth-talker?

30
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:32,708
No one... but you came
here for a reason.

31
00:03:34,750 --> 00:03:36,541
[NAGI] I first noticed it
dangling around your neck

32
00:03:36,625 --> 00:03:39,750
while bracing across
from you on the mat.

33
00:03:39,833 --> 00:03:42,500
And when I heard
it jingle, I knew...

34
00:03:42,583 --> 00:03:44,125
There's quite a bit
more to this gal

35
00:03:44,208 --> 00:03:46,250
than her chops
as a warrior.

36
00:03:46,333 --> 00:03:49,458
Call it a hunch.

37
00:03:49,541 --> 00:03:52,291
Which is why I want you
to be our number two.

38
00:03:52,375 --> 00:03:54,708
All because of a
cheap little bell, huh?

39
00:03:54,791 --> 00:03:56,500
That's right.

40
00:03:59,083 --> 00:04:04,166
[KARAKO LAUGHS]

41
00:04:07,541 --> 00:04:11,083
God, what a fool...

42
00:04:11,166 --> 00:04:12,666
Did they all get across?

43
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,416
[NECRO MACRO WHIRS]

44
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,958
Asshole.

45
00:04:17,333 --> 00:04:20,166
[KARAKO THINKING]
What did I want outta life?

46
00:04:20,250 --> 00:04:21,875
I wanted you.

47
00:04:21,958 --> 00:04:25,125
[STEAM HISSES]

48
00:04:31,375 --> 00:04:33,666
[NECRO MACRO WHIRS]

49
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:36,166
[KARAKO]
Tough titty, huh?

50
00:04:36,250 --> 00:04:41,916
As it turns out I'm a stone-cold
bitch on offense and defense.

51
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,041
[KARAKO THINKING]
Know what, Nagi?!

52
00:04:44,125 --> 00:04:46,250
Even if what we're
fighting for is bunk...

53
00:04:46,333 --> 00:04:48,875
nothing but a
stupid pipe-dream...!

54
00:04:48,958 --> 00:04:50,916
Goddamn it! I'm all in.

55
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:53,125
I might get to make
it outside again...

56
00:04:53,208 --> 00:04:55,208
but if I die right here...

57
00:04:55,291 --> 00:04:57,333
So fucking be it.

58
00:04:58,708 --> 00:05:02,000
[CRASHING SOUND]

59
00:05:35,708 --> 00:05:37,583
Karako's okay back there...

60
00:05:37,666 --> 00:05:39,208
She is, right?

61
00:05:39,291 --> 00:05:43,125
She's tough... Ain't no
point worrying about her.

62
00:05:43,208 --> 00:05:44,916
[GANTA]
Yeah, but...

63
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,750
I mean, we just
left her behind...

64
00:05:51,333 --> 00:05:53,083
Look, Ganta...

65
00:05:53,166 --> 00:05:55,666
Karako knew what was at stake.

66
00:05:58,416 --> 00:06:00,875
Right.

67
00:06:00,958 --> 00:06:03,208
The Undertakers are
probably on their way...

68
00:06:03,291 --> 00:06:05,291
I sure don't wanna be
here when they show up.

69
00:06:05,375 --> 00:06:07,458
They may not
be clued in yet...

70
00:06:07,541 --> 00:06:10,125
If they were, this whole
block would be on lockdown.

71
00:06:10,208 --> 00:06:12,000
Besides,
Wakabayashi and Miyako

72
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:16,083
are ready to lead them
on a wild goose chase.

73
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:18,291
[HARUMI] This is the
elevator we need to take...

74
00:06:18,375 --> 00:06:21,250
It's our one-way ticket
outta Deadman Wonderland.

75
00:06:21,333 --> 00:06:23,708
Sounds pretty
straightforward...

76
00:06:23,791 --> 00:06:25,875
But Nagi and Rokuro
have to send it down

77
00:06:25,958 --> 00:06:27,750
from the control
room, don't they?

78
00:06:27,833 --> 00:06:29,291
That's right kid.

79
00:06:29,375 --> 00:06:31,666
If those doors
open, then we know

80
00:06:31,750 --> 00:06:35,166
those two were able to
get the job done up there.

81
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:41,958
[NAGI AND ROKURO
BREATHE HEAVILY]

82
00:06:46,041 --> 00:06:48,625
How you holding up,
Rokuro...? You good?

83
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:50,875
Yeah, I'm fine.

84
00:06:50,958 --> 00:06:53,375
Then let's get that
service elevator activated...

85
00:06:53,458 --> 00:06:55,083
If all is going
well down there,

86
00:06:55,166 --> 00:06:57,250
they should be waiting
for it even as we speak.

87
00:06:57,333 --> 00:06:59,666
[SQUEAKING]

88
00:07:10,250 --> 00:07:11,916
Little girl...

89
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:15,958
What on earth are
you doing in here?

90
00:07:16,041 --> 00:07:17,500
It's a pleasure
to meet you...

91
00:07:17,583 --> 00:07:19,208
My name is Hibana.

92
00:07:19,291 --> 00:07:21,166
Listen to you... 

93
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:24,416
That is a very polite greeting
from someone so young...

94
00:07:24,500 --> 00:07:25,916
How old are you, dear?

95
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,416
I'm actually in the 
second-grade, mister...

96
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:30,416
And I just
finished my homework...

97
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:33,416
So it's time to do my
chores like a young lady.

98
00:07:33,500 --> 00:07:35,291
The plot thickens,
it seems... 

99
00:07:35,375 --> 00:07:37,791
I daresay you're
lost... Rokuro...

100
00:07:37,875 --> 00:07:39,333
Send down the
elevator, would you?

101
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:41,041
I'm sure the
others are there.

102
00:07:41,125 --> 00:07:43,250
[ROKURO] Hmm...

103
00:07:44,375 --> 00:07:46,625
Listen--you aren't
safe here...

104
00:07:46,708 --> 00:07:49,333
I think you ought
to come with us.

105
00:07:53,208 --> 00:07:54,666
[ROKURO LAUGHS]

106
00:07:54,750 --> 00:07:57,791
Rokuro... What are
you waiting for?!

107
00:07:57,875 --> 00:07:58,958
Sorry, fearless leader,

108
00:07:59,041 --> 00:08:03,041
but there's been a
slight change of plans.

109
00:08:03,125 --> 00:08:04,625
What are
you talking about?

110
00:08:04,708 --> 00:08:07,750
[CRACKING]

111
00:08:09,458 --> 00:08:12,875
Shoulda checked my work when
you had me crunch the numbers.

112
00:08:15,208 --> 00:08:17,083
[HIBANA]
Down you go...!

113
00:08:29,666 --> 00:08:33,458
I'm the commander of the
3rd Undertaker Battalion...

114
00:08:33,541 --> 00:08:38,750
I'm here because you...
have been a very naughty boy.

115
00:08:38,833 --> 00:08:40,708
Do what you must.

116
00:08:44,666 --> 00:08:48,041
Yet another thing
I'll regret having to do.

117
00:08:48,125 --> 00:08:50,291
My apologies, little one.

118
00:08:57,166 --> 00:08:58,500
My branch of sin!

119
00:08:59,833 --> 00:09:02,208
[CRASHING SOUND]

120
00:09:05,708 --> 00:09:07,708
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

121
00:09:13,458 --> 00:09:15,541
Now all your sins
will be burned down

122
00:09:15,625 --> 00:09:18,916
to ash in the 21st
dimension of Isgorchia...

123
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:21,458
So then you won't have
the naughty blood anymore...

124
00:09:21,541 --> 00:09:23,666
And nobody'll
call you the Owl... 

125
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:27,958
because you won't have
special powers after we're done.

126
00:09:28,041 --> 00:09:30,458
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

127
00:09:33,291 --> 00:09:34,458
[NAGI THINKING]
Blood negation...

128
00:09:34,541 --> 00:09:36,833
Ganta warned us of this...

129
00:09:41,916 --> 00:09:43,833
[NAGI]
You bastard.

130
00:09:43,916 --> 00:09:47,208
You manipulated the
footage... didn't you?

131
00:09:50,333 --> 00:09:52,958
[HIBANA]
Surprise, mister!

132
00:09:53,041 --> 00:09:54,750
Wanna know a secret?

133
00:09:54,833 --> 00:09:57,125
There's a thing in my
sword called Worm Eater.

134
00:09:57,208 --> 00:09:59,625
It oxidizes the
virus in your blood. 

135
00:09:59,708 --> 00:10:01,708
You can attack me with
your branch of sin,

136
00:10:01,791 --> 00:10:03,583
but it's just
gonna disintegrate.

137
00:10:03,666 --> 00:10:06,458
All us Undertakers
have it in our weapons.

138
00:10:06,541 --> 00:10:09,458
That's pretty
nifty, isn't it?!

139
00:10:09,541 --> 00:10:10,833
Thanks for explaining.

140
00:10:10,916 --> 00:10:12,083
[HIBANA LAUGHS]

141
00:10:12,166 --> 00:10:15,166
Well, a lady is
honest with her foe.

142
00:10:15,250 --> 00:10:17,416
[ROKURO LAUGHS]

143
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:20,875
You're at a disadvantage...
Wouldn't you agree?

144
00:10:20,958 --> 00:10:23,583
The Undertakers all have
their brains bad-touched... 

145
00:10:23,666 --> 00:10:25,208
That's where they
wrench out their mercy

146
00:10:25,291 --> 00:10:27,500
and empathy and
all that shit...

147
00:10:27,583 --> 00:10:31,916
So how 'bout we make
this easy on everyone?

148
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:35,166
[NAGI THINKING]
Failure is not an option.

149
00:10:35,250 --> 00:10:37,625
Their dreams...

150
00:10:37,708 --> 00:10:41,541
And mine... Too much
hangs in the balance!

151
00:10:57,250 --> 00:10:59,166
Someone didn't listen!

152
00:10:59,250 --> 00:11:03,750
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

153
00:11:28,875 --> 00:11:30,208
[OOTAKE]
What's keeping 'em?

154
00:11:30,291 --> 00:11:32,291
It hasn't moved
an inch yet.

155
00:11:32,375 --> 00:11:34,666
Oh Nagi...
and Rokuro...

156
00:11:34,750 --> 00:11:37,041
...please be okay.

157
00:11:40,625 --> 00:11:42,333
[GANTA THINKING]
Now what...?

158
00:11:45,416 --> 00:11:50,375
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

159
00:11:56,583 --> 00:11:58,250
[HIBANA]
Shame on you, mister...!

160
00:11:58,333 --> 00:12:02,166
Running around,
getting blood on everything!

161
00:12:02,250 --> 00:12:06,041
But it's nothing that a little
tough love can't fix right up!

162
00:12:09,583 --> 00:12:11,458
[NAGI THINKING]
You little imp...!

163
00:12:12,625 --> 00:12:14,875
You need a lot
more punishing huh...

164
00:12:14,958 --> 00:12:16,708
But Genkaku told me that

165
00:12:16,791 --> 00:12:19,083
killing you would
be a big no-no...

166
00:12:21,500 --> 00:12:23,541
[ROKURO] You keep thumpin'
the shit outta him...

167
00:12:23,625 --> 00:12:25,916
he's gonna die whether
you want him to or not.

168
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,000
[ROKURO LAUGHS]

169
00:12:28,083 --> 00:12:29,708
[HIBANA]
No going easy on him!

170
00:12:29,791 --> 00:12:31,125
Listen, you!

171
00:12:31,208 --> 00:12:33,625
You're getting punished
until I hear a proper apology!

172
00:12:33,708 --> 00:12:36,541
Heh! She don't beat
around the bush, does she?

173
00:12:36,625 --> 00:12:37,750
You're might wanna
say you're sorry

174
00:12:37,833 --> 00:12:39,416
before she
breaks your neck.

175
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:41,583
I realize that you're
not my daughter... 

176
00:12:41,666 --> 00:12:43,083
But I'm not about
to just overlook...

177
00:12:43,166 --> 00:12:46,166
such ill-mannered
behavior from one so young.

178
00:12:46,250 --> 00:12:49,041
How about... I give
you the Lingering Death!

179
00:12:49,125 --> 00:12:53,041
Uh-oh...
She's about to get creative.

180
00:12:53,125 --> 00:12:54,416
Don't know what that is...? 

181
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:57,291
You shoulda hit
the books a little harder!

182
00:12:57,375 --> 00:12:58,833
Fine I'll tell you.

183
00:12:58,916 --> 00:13:01,750
The Lingering Death is a method
of execution that China used

184
00:13:01,833 --> 00:13:03,750
until late into
the Ching Dynasty...

185
00:13:03,833 --> 00:13:05,083
They'd cut a person apart,

186
00:13:05,166 --> 00:13:07,250
but they'd be super
careful about it...

187
00:13:07,333 --> 00:13:10,541
First, they'd slice the
flesh off the person's chest...

188
00:13:10,625 --> 00:13:13,291
And then, off of the
arms... and the stomach...

189
00:13:13,375 --> 00:13:16,916
an' thighs...
even the bottom...

190
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:20,000
I wonder how many cuts
I can give you?

191
00:13:31,208 --> 00:13:35,208
If I'm really careful, I betcha
I can cut you 3,000 times!

192
00:13:35,291 --> 00:13:40,125
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

193
00:13:45,208 --> 00:13:47,041
If you're worried about
bleeding out, mister...

194
00:13:47,125 --> 00:13:48,416
...don't be!

195
00:13:48,500 --> 00:13:51,166
Cause you're gonna get
scared in a minute or two...

196
00:13:51,250 --> 00:13:54,166
and scared people don't
bleed nearly as much!

197
00:13:54,250 --> 00:13:55,916
[ROKURO YAWNS]

198
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,083
I'm telling ya,
the dude's gonna die.

199
00:13:58,166 --> 00:13:59,375
He'll be okay!

200
00:13:59,458 --> 00:14:01,250
Without pain,
how can we ever become

201
00:14:01,333 --> 00:14:04,375
the upstanding citizens
we're supposed to be?!

202
00:14:05,416 --> 00:14:06,583
That's what Mama thought,

203
00:14:06,666 --> 00:14:09,208
and I think I
turned out pretty well!

204
00:14:09,291 --> 00:14:12,875
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

205
00:14:12,958 --> 00:14:16,083
You'll mature into a perfect
gentleman before you know it...

206
00:14:16,166 --> 00:14:19,583
Prob'ly even before I
even lop off your face!

207
00:14:19,666 --> 00:14:22,500
That was you, wasn't it...
a couple of years ago...

208
00:14:22,583 --> 00:14:23,708
The one who cut her whole

209
00:14:23,791 --> 00:14:25,833
kindergarten class
into ribbons...

210
00:14:25,916 --> 00:14:30,083
Well as a lady... it is my
duty to punish the wicked.

211
00:14:30,166 --> 00:14:33,666
"Lady"... you said...?

212
00:14:33,750 --> 00:14:37,291
A lady would never
butcher children.

213
00:14:37,375 --> 00:14:40,875
What you are, under the
very best of circumstances...

214
00:14:40,958 --> 00:14:43,916
is a mewling little
hellion of a girl.

215
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,958
I feel pity for you...

216
00:14:46,041 --> 00:14:49,041
A tattered scrap of
humanity--that's all you are.

217
00:14:49,125 --> 00:14:52,000
Mama's special
little punching-bag.

218
00:14:58,875 --> 00:15:02,375
[HIBANA]
I am not... a little brat!

219
00:15:03,916 --> 00:15:06,458
Hibana is... a lady!

220
00:15:06,541 --> 00:15:09,166
[CRASHING SOUNDS]

221
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:12,625
[HIBANA GRUNTS]

222
00:15:12,708 --> 00:15:17,666
[NAGI GRUNTS IN PAIN]

223
00:15:20,875 --> 00:15:24,166
[HIBANA'S MOTHER] Wretched girl!
You've wet the bed, again!

224
00:15:24,250 --> 00:15:25,791
As punishment, we must return

225
00:15:25,875 --> 00:15:27,750
the piss to
the 17th dimension--

226
00:15:27,833 --> 00:15:30,875
to the seat of the hizamoro,
from whence it came!

227
00:15:30,958 --> 00:15:33,500
[HIBANA]
Yes, Mama... I'm sorry.

228
00:15:33,583 --> 00:15:35,041
[HIBANA'S MOTHER]
Wretched girl!

229
00:15:35,125 --> 00:15:38,416
How dare you vomit up
perfectly good mushrooms?!

230
00:15:38,500 --> 00:15:39,833
As punishment, we have to seal

231
00:15:39,916 --> 00:15:43,458
the three holes within
Battenoro's orbit at once!

232
00:15:43,541 --> 00:15:45,708
[HIBANA]
Yes, Mama... I'm sorry.

233
00:15:45,791 --> 00:15:48,666
[HIBANA GRUNTS]

234
00:15:48,750 --> 00:15:51,125
I did punish them
properly, didn't I?

235
00:15:51,208 --> 00:15:52,500
My mama taught me...!

236
00:15:52,583 --> 00:15:56,375
She taught me so well,
I taught her right back!

237
00:16:00,375 --> 00:16:02,250
I don't pee the bed anymore!

238
00:16:02,333 --> 00:16:04,208
I love mushrooms--I love 'em!

239
00:16:04,291 --> 00:16:05,958
[NAGI GRUNTS]

240
00:16:06,041 --> 00:16:08,791
I'm a lady, just like Mama!

241
00:16:08,875 --> 00:16:11,125
[NAGI SCREAMS]

242
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:18,666
You call that
punishment, do you?

243
00:16:20,166 --> 00:16:22,625
Don't make me laugh.

244
00:16:22,708 --> 00:16:26,291
I won't be felled by
a couple of scratches...

245
00:16:26,375 --> 00:16:29,166
What kind of a weakling
do you take me for?!

246
00:16:29,250 --> 00:16:30,541
[HIBANA YELLS]

247
00:16:38,291 --> 00:16:40,750
Stop it or I'm
gonna cut off that one!

248
00:16:40,833 --> 00:16:42,250
Sure you
wanna do that?

249
00:16:42,333 --> 00:16:43,333
Huh...?

250
00:16:43,416 --> 00:16:45,958
[NAGI] Should've
put your toys away...

251
00:16:46,041 --> 00:16:47,833
[HIBANA YELLS WORRIEDLY]

252
00:16:47,916 --> 00:16:52,000
I apologize for what
I'm about to do to you.

253
00:16:52,083 --> 00:16:53,916
You little bitch.

254
00:16:56,583 --> 00:16:57,541
Here we go.

255
00:16:57,625 --> 00:17:00,333
They pulled it off! 
Heh! Good job!

256
00:17:00,416 --> 00:17:02,291
[KOSUGI]
Let's get a move on, guys!

257
00:17:13,291 --> 00:17:16,708
Rokuro and Nagi
sure delivered!

258
00:17:16,791 --> 00:17:18,208
You hang onto
that data chip...

259
00:17:18,291 --> 00:17:19,500
Nice and tight.

260
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:21,000
[GANTA] I will!

261
00:17:21,083 --> 00:17:23,291
[OOTAKE] I wonder how I'm
gonna get by on the outside...

262
00:17:23,375 --> 00:17:25,041
Come an' work at my factory.

263
00:17:25,125 --> 00:17:27,125
Hell, maybe I should
tag along too...

264
00:17:27,208 --> 00:17:28,583
Finally get to 
scope out this wife

265
00:17:28,666 --> 00:17:30,000
you're always
going on about.

266
00:17:30,083 --> 00:17:32,166
Don't blame me
if ya fall in love!

267
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,583
[YAMAZAKI LAUGHS]

268
00:17:33,666 --> 00:17:36,041
Yeah, but what if she
falls in love with Ueshima?

269
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:37,583
[ENDOU LAUGHS]

270
00:17:37,666 --> 00:17:39,000
If my wife is steppin' out...

271
00:17:39,083 --> 00:17:41,375
it's gonna be with
a hotter guy than him!

272
00:17:41,458 --> 00:17:44,208
[GROUP LAUGHS]

273
00:17:44,291 --> 00:17:46,666
[GENKAKU]
Hey assholes, laugh it up!

274
00:17:46,750 --> 00:17:48,916
Think it's time
I played you off.

275
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:50,208
[GUNSHOTS]

276
00:17:50,291 --> 00:17:52,875
[YELLING]

277
00:17:55,583 --> 00:17:56,708
Hmm...?

278
00:17:56,791 --> 00:17:59,541
What the fuck, fellas?
Where's the albino?

279
00:17:59,625 --> 00:18:00,750
[KOSUGI]
Damn Undertaker!

280
00:18:00,833 --> 00:18:03,416
Who the hell do
you think you are?!

281
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:06,541
Duuude... Uber-monk.

282
00:18:06,625 --> 00:18:07,791
[ENDOU YELLS]

283
00:18:09,583 --> 00:18:12,458
The branch of sin...
It didn't--

284
00:18:12,541 --> 00:18:13,708
[OHARA] Harumi!

285
00:18:13,791 --> 00:18:16,458
[FIGHTING SOUNDS]

286
00:18:18,625 --> 00:18:20,166
[GANTA YELLS]

287
00:18:20,250 --> 00:18:20,708
[GUNSHOT]

288
00:18:20,791 --> 00:18:22,208
[AKIYAMA GROANS]

289
00:18:29,416 --> 00:18:32,416
[ROKURO] I'm impressed,
not gonna lie...

290
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:34,250
The odds of you actually
defeating that kid

291
00:18:34,333 --> 00:18:36,041
and sending the elevator
down to the others

292
00:18:36,125 --> 00:18:39,291
were something
like fifty to one.

293
00:18:39,375 --> 00:18:41,750
Am I to assume...

294
00:18:41,833 --> 00:18:44,958
you sicced the Undertakers
on the others as well?

295
00:18:45,041 --> 00:18:46,916
[ROKURO]
Dude, you have to ask?

296
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:48,500
Whatever you do...

297
00:18:48,583 --> 00:18:50,666
I know the others
will manage to smuggle

298
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:53,041
that data-chip
out of this place.

299
00:18:53,125 --> 00:18:57,083
[ROKURO] They've got a
one-fifth of one percent chance.

300
00:18:57,166 --> 00:19:01,375
More than enough...
when dreams are on the line...

301
00:19:01,458 --> 00:19:04,500
Even if the odds
were infinitely worse...

302
00:19:04,583 --> 00:19:06,041
That's a bet I would take.

303
00:19:06,125 --> 00:19:07,333
[ROKURO LAUGHS]

304
00:19:07,416 --> 00:19:09,625
You must've hit your
head when you fell down...

305
00:19:09,708 --> 00:19:11,583
'Cause I've been busting
my ass to make sure

306
00:19:11,666 --> 00:19:14,291
that never fucking happens,
you sorry sack o' shit!

307
00:19:14,375 --> 00:19:16,583
Tamaki knew what you
were up to all along.

308
00:19:16,666 --> 00:19:19,333
You played right into his hands.

309
00:19:19,416 --> 00:19:22,041
Just so you know,
my calculations are legit.

310
00:19:22,125 --> 00:19:24,000
I mean, there were
a lot of easier ways

311
00:19:24,083 --> 00:19:25,541
to take Scar Chain out...

312
00:19:25,625 --> 00:19:28,333
but the boss insisted
on a spectacle...

313
00:19:28,416 --> 00:19:32,166
Man... Undertakers are killing
your friends even as we speak.

314
00:19:32,250 --> 00:19:33,250
[NAGI SHUDDERS]

315
00:19:33,333 --> 00:19:35,500
[GANTA GRUNTS]

316
00:19:36,958 --> 00:19:38,208
What was that for?

317
00:19:38,291 --> 00:19:41,750
You protect this data-chip
with your life, Ganta!

318
00:19:41,833 --> 00:19:44,000
Just get it to
the outside world!

319
00:19:44,083 --> 00:19:45,000
[KOSUGI GASPS]

320
00:19:46,291 --> 00:19:47,583
[KOSUGI YELLS]

321
00:19:50,958 --> 00:19:53,875
Show them... the truth...

322
00:19:55,458 --> 00:19:58,750
You are Scar Chain... now...

323
00:20:02,500 --> 00:20:03,916
Ganta!

324
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:06,208
Does freedom look
like that to you, Ganta?

325
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:08,041
Something harsh?

326
00:20:09,125 --> 00:20:11,291
[GANTA THINKING]
They gave their lives...

327
00:20:11,375 --> 00:20:13,291
everything they had...

328
00:20:13,375 --> 00:20:15,291
for the sake of the truth!

329
00:20:17,125 --> 00:20:21,458
Even if it kills me...
the world is gonna know!

330
00:20:26,291 --> 00:20:29,375
[NAGI GRUNTS]

331
00:20:32,375 --> 00:20:34,083
[ALARM SOUNDS]

332
00:20:34,166 --> 00:20:39,708
[NAGI] If any...
anyone... can hear me...

333
00:20:39,791 --> 00:20:44,166
Please, just... listen...

334
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:46,583
I wanna sleep but
it's too noisy...

335
00:20:46,666 --> 00:20:49,041
An' I'm so hungry...

336
00:20:50,916 --> 00:20:52,541
Hey, Ganta?

337
00:20:53,958 --> 00:20:57,000
Huh?... Hey, who're you?

338
00:21:00,666 --> 00:21:02,666
[OOTAKE SCREAMS]

339
00:21:07,166 --> 00:21:08,333
[GANTA GASPS]

340
00:21:08,416 --> 00:21:09,541
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

341
00:21:09,625 --> 00:21:11,625
[GUNSHOTS]

342
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:14,666
[GANTA YELLS]

343
00:21:15,875 --> 00:21:17,416
You might want to
think of a back-up plan

344
00:21:17,500 --> 00:21:19,708
if you're waitin'
for Aceman.

345
00:21:19,791 --> 00:21:22,041
Speaking of everyone's
favorite superhero,

346
00:21:22,125 --> 00:21:26,083
didja know the series was
supposed to end differently?

347
00:21:26,166 --> 00:21:27,625
[GANTA YELLS]

348
00:21:27,708 --> 00:21:29,541
The villains all put
their heads together,

349
00:21:29,625 --> 00:21:33,166
and decide to kill
everyone but Aceman...

350
00:21:33,250 --> 00:21:36,250
They proceed to stack those
bastards up like cordwood.

351
00:21:36,333 --> 00:21:38,166
Shut up...

352
00:21:38,250 --> 00:21:41,250
I think they should have
aired it as-is, don't you?

353
00:21:41,333 --> 00:21:42,833
Why sugar-coat it?

354
00:21:42,916 --> 00:21:44,833
Leave me alone!

355
00:21:44,916 --> 00:21:47,375
Our lives are nothing
more than suffering.

356
00:21:47,458 --> 00:21:50,250
Why hammer it into the
kiddies' heads one at a time

357
00:21:50,333 --> 00:21:52,791
when you can teach
'em all at once?!

358
00:21:52,875 --> 00:21:54,208
[GENKAKU LAUGHS]

359
00:21:56,750 --> 00:22:01,000
Sorry, Genkaku...
But it's time to go.

360
00:22:01,083 --> 00:22:03,000
Catch ya later, kid.

361
00:22:05,833 --> 00:22:08,041
You'll get your private show.

362
00:22:08,125 --> 00:22:11,291
I got a song
that'll knock you dead.

363
00:22:13,833 --> 00:22:15,250
What the
hell was that?!

364
00:22:15,333 --> 00:22:16,916
C'mon, you guys--
this is our chance!

365
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:19,083
Ganta, it's time to go!

366
00:22:19,166 --> 00:22:19,916
[GANTA] Okay!

367
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:21,958
[STEAM HISSES]

368
00:22:24,541 --> 00:22:26,791
Shiro, what were
you doing in there?!

369
00:22:26,875 --> 00:22:28,666
I told you to wait!

370
00:22:28,750 --> 00:22:30,458
What's going on?
Why do you look scared?

371
00:22:30,541 --> 00:22:31,666
Listen, Ganta...!

372
00:22:31,750 --> 00:22:33,666
You gotta give me the
data chip right now!

373
00:22:33,750 --> 00:22:36,041
Hold on, what're you...?

374
00:22:36,958 --> 00:22:38,541
[GANTA] Wait, how do
you know about the--?!

375
00:22:38,625 --> 00:22:40,750
Hey...! Gimmie that!

376
00:22:40,833 --> 00:22:42,500
Shiro!

377
00:22:43,166 --> 00:22:44,833
[SHIRO GRUNTS]

378
00:22:49,125 --> 00:22:51,833
[EXPLOSION]

379
00:22:53,416 --> 00:22:55,291
[GROUP GASPS]

380
00:23:03,791 --> 00:23:07,333
Ganta... I'm so
glad you're okay!

381
00:23:08,250 --> 00:23:13,208
♪ closing song ♪

382
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,166
[MAKINA]
Insanity feeds on itself...

383
00:24:41,250 --> 00:24:43,541
gives birth to itself anew...

384
00:24:43,625 --> 00:24:46,708
It doesn't matter how much
the weak piss and moan,

385
00:24:46,791 --> 00:24:48,958
they still end up
as cannon fodder...

386
00:24:49,041 --> 00:24:53,041
Only the strong survive...
Remember that, Ganta.

